{"type":"question","id":1982,"title":"[经略新闻话题] 抗生素污染危害如何？在共匪不作为情况下，自我有何措施降低污染带来的危害？","uid":798,"topics":[1088,847],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.redd.it/i15inj0ccuf21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.redd.it/i15inj0ccuf21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.redd.it/i15inj0ccuf21.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.redd.it/i15inj0ccuf21.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n抗生素已经成了世界范围内公共卫生领域的重大问题之一。近期一份抗生素污染地图揭露了隐藏在我们食物体系中的惊人事实，每年有数万吨抗生素经由养殖动物和我们的身体，进入水土环境，致使各种病菌严重抗药，鸡鸭猪牛鱼全部沦陷。威胁已经在人体中暴露。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.redd.it/jxhmx1xeduf21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.redd.it/jxhmx1xeduf21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.redd.it/jxhmx1xeduf21.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.redd.it/jxhmx1xeduf21.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/4832/comments/apax8t","date":"2019-02-12","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}